org.springframework.web.client.reactive

接口 ClientResponse


  • public interface ClientResponse
    Represents an HTTP response, as returned by the WebClient. Access to headers and body is offered by ClientResponse.Headers and body(BodyExtractor) respectively.
    从以下版本开始:
    5.0
    作者:
    Brian Clozel, Arjen Poutsma

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 接口和说明
      static interface  ClientResponse.Headers
      Represents the headers of the HTTP response.
